Package dataTypes

Class parameters

java.lang.Object
dataTypes.parameters
public class parameters
extends java.lang.Object
Represents parameters for model simulation, optimization, etc.
Author:
Sudesh Agrawal (sudesh@utexas.edu). Last Updated: October 1, 2020.
